name: In Melancholic Ocean
description:
✦ 1st Artwork for Obscure Delirium Series ✦

Obscure Delirium is a series made to capture the period when losing awareness of oneself and the surrounding ✾

This animated digital painting tries to illustrate how someone could easily feel floundering and incapable of doing anything while tormented by seeing everything pass so quickly and slipped through his fingers.
